      ja: {"term":"楽観的排他制御","kana":"ラッカンテキハイタセイギョ","note":"データの更新競合が少ないと仮定し、ロックを掛けずに更新時にバージョン番号などで競合を確認・検知する制御。"},
      zh: {"term":"乐观并发控制","explanation":"假设数据冲突极少发生，读写时不锁定数据，只在事务提交时通过版本号或时间戳校验是否被他人修改的并发控制机制，简称 OCC。"},
      en: {"term":"Optimistic Concurrency Control","explanation":"A concurrency control method for database transactions that assumes multiple transactions can frequently complete without interfering with each other, validating data at commit time."},
      my: {"term":"မျှော်လင့်ချက်ရှိသော ပူးတွဲထိန်းချုပ်မှုစနစ်","explanation":"ဒေတာပြိုင်ဆိုင်မှုနည်းပါးမည်ဟု ယူဆကာ ကြိုတင်ပိတ်ဆို့မထားဘဲ commit လုပ်ချိန်တွင်သာ version စစ်ဆေးသည့် စနစ် (OCC)。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Kiểm soát truy cập đồng thời lạc quan","explanation":"Phương pháp không khóa dữ liệu trước, chỉ kiểm tra xung đột thông qua số phiên bản tại thời điểm xác nhận giao dịch (commit)。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Contrôle d'accès concurrent optimiste","explanation":"Méthode de gestion de concurrence (OCC) ne posant pas de verrous, vérifiant la non-collision des données lors de la validation。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["OCC","Optimistic Locking"],
      related: [],
