      zh: {"term":"集成测试阶段","explanation":"软件工程测试阶段。将已通过单元测试的多个模块组合在一起进行测试，着重验证各模块接口交互与协作的数据正确性。"},
      en: {"term":"Integration Testing Stage","explanation":"A level of software testing where individual units/modules are combined and tested as a group to expose faults in interaction."},
