      zh: {"term":"回归测试阶段","explanation":"软件质量保证阶段。在软件升级、修 Bug 或变更后，重新运行已有测试用例，确保修改未导致既有功能受到破坏。"},
      en: {"term":"Regression Testing Stage","explanation":"A type of software testing that runs existing test cases to confirm that recent code changes have not adversely affected existing features."},
