      ja: {"term":"著作権保護 / 著作権法","kana":"ちょさくけんほう","note":"文芸、学術、美術、音楽、またはプログラムなどの著作物を創作した者に与えられる、無方式主義の権利保護。"},
      zh: {"term":"著作权保护","explanation":"法律赋予文学、艺术、科学及计算机软件等作品创作者的专有权利保护，采用无须登记自动产生的无方式主义。"},
      en: {"term":"Copyright Protection","explanation":"A legal right that grants the creator of an original work exclusive rights for its use and distribution, typically for a limited time."},
      my: {"term":"မူပိုင်ခွင့် ကာကွယ်မှုစနစ်","explanation":"စာပေ၊ အနုပညာ၊ သိပ္ပံနှင့် ကွန်ပျူတာဆော့ဖ်ဝဲလ်စသော မူရင်းဖန်တီးသူများအား ၎င်းတို့၏လက်ရာများအတွက် ဥပဒေအရ အကာအကွယ်ပေးသည့် စနစ်。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Bảo hộ bản quyền","explanation":"Quyền pháp lý bảo vệ tác giả của các tác phẩm gốc như văn học, nghệ thuật và phần mềm máy tính khỏi sự sao chép bất hợp pháp。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Protection des droits d'auteur","explanation":"Droit légal (propriété intellectuelle) protégeant les créateurs d'œuvres originales (y compris logicielles) contre l'exploitation non autorisée。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["Copyright","author's right"],
      related: [],
      example: {"text":"Software code is protected by copyright protection immediately upon its creation."},
