      ja: {"term":"不正競争防止法","kana":"フセイキョウソウボウシホウ","note":"事業者間の公正な競争と営業秘密の保護を目的とし、コピー商品の販売や他人のブランドの無断利用などを規制する法律。"},
      zh: {"term":"反不正当竞争法","explanation":"旨在维护市场公平竞争秩序，禁止混淆商品来源、窃取他人商业秘密以及散布虚假信息损害对手商誉等行为的法律规范。"},
      en: {"term":"Unfair Competition Prevention Act","explanation":"A law aimed at securing fair competition among businesses, protecting trade secrets, and prohibiting misleading representations."},
      my: {"term":"မတရားယှဉ်ပြိုင်မှု ကာကွယ်ရေးဥပဒေ","explanation":"လုပ်ငန်းများအကြား မတရားသဖြင့် တုပထုတ်လုပ်ခြင်းနှင့် စီးပွားရေးလျှို့ဝှက်ချက်များ ခိုးယူခြင်းကို တားဆီးရန် ပြဋ္ဌာန်းထားသည့် ဥပဒေ。","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Luật chống cạnh tranh không lành mạnh","explanation":"Đạo luật nhằm đảm bảo cạnh tranh công bằng giữa các doanh nghiệp, bảo vệ bí mật kinh doanh và ngăn chặn các hành vi gian lận thương mại。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Loi sur la prévention de la concurrence déloyale","explanation":"Législation protégeant les secrets d'affaires et interdisant les pratiques commerciales abusives (contrefaçon, parasitisme)。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["UCPA","unfair competition law"],
      related: ["patent_right"],
      example: {"text":"Under the Unfair Competition Prevention Act, stealing a competitor's customer list is illegal."},
