      zh: {"term":"分布式数据库","explanation":"物理上制造分散在网络不同节点，但在逻辑上属于统一管理，对外呈现单一视图的数据库系统。"},
      en: {"term":"Distributed Database","explanation":"A database that is under the control of a central DBMS in which the storage devices are not all attached to a common processor, distributed over network."},
