      zh: {"term":"直接内存访问控制器","explanation":"计算机体系结构芯片。允许外设（如硬盘、网卡）在完全不通过 CPU 干预的情况下，直接与物理主内存交换高吞吐量数据，简称 DMAC。"},
      en: {"term":"Direct Memory Access Controller","explanation":"A hardware device that allows peripheral subsystems to read from or write to primary memory directly, bypassing the CPU to increase system speed."},
      my: {"term":"တိုက်ရိုက်မှတ်ဉာဏ်ဝင်ရောက်မှု ထိန်းချုပ်ကိရိယာ","explanation":"CPU ၏ ကြားဝင်ဆောင်ရွက်မှုမပါဘဲ ပြင်ပပစ္စည်းများနှင့် RAM အကြား ဒေတာများကို တိုက်ရိုက်မြန်ဆန်စွာ ကူးယူပေးသည့် ဟာ့ဒ်ဝဲ (DMAC)။","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Bộ điều khiển truy cập bộ nhớ trực tiếp","explanation":"Chip phần cứng (DMAC) cho phép các thiết bị ngoại vi trao đổi dữ liệu trực tiếp với RAM mà không cần CPU xử lý。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Contrôleur d'accès direct à la mémoire","explanation":"Composant matériel (DMAC) gérant les transferts directs de données entre périphériques et RAM sans passer par le CPU。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["DMAC","DMA controller"],
      related: [],
      example: {"text":"The network card offloads data transmission to the direct memory access controller to reduce CPU load."},
      source: "project-glossary-v2"
