      my: {"term":"Hard Disk Drive တည်ဆောက်ပုံ","explanation":"လည်ပတ်နေသော သံလိုက်ချပ်ပြား (platters) များနှင့် ၎င်းပေါ်ရှိ ဖတ်ရေးခေါင်း (heads) များသုံးပြီး ဒေတာများသိမ်းသည့် စက်မှုပုံစံ HDD။","needsReview":true},
      vi: {"term":"Cấu trúc ổ đĩa cứng cơ học HDD","explanation":"Thiết bị lưu trữ dữ liệu từ tính sử dụng các phiến đĩa quay tròn và đầu đọc/ghi chuyển động vật lý。","needsReview":true},
      fr: {"term":"Structure d'un disque dur HDD / Hard Disk Drive","explanation":"Composants mécaniques d'un disque dur (plateaux magnétiques en rotation, bras de lecture/écriture) sujet aux chocs。","needsReview":true},
      aliases: ["HDD","Hard Disk Drive"],
      related: ["solid_state_drive_structure"],
