      zh: {"term":"HTTP 2xx 成功状态码","explanation":"HTTP 协议响应状态码。表示客户端发送的请求已被服务器成功接收、理解并成功处理，如 200 OK、201 Created。"},
      en: {"term":"HTTP Status Codes 2xx","explanation":"A class of HTTP response status codes indicating that the client's request was successfully received, understood, and accepted."},
